Are you an existing client looking to access your policy information or are you interested in finding out about Clientèle products? If you fall in either one of these categories, look no further than the Clientèle App.

With this App, you will have access to all our key functionalities at your fingertips and from the comfort of your home or office. This is convenience at its best, with just a few clicks, you will be able to perform key functions on this App.

At the core of our strategy as a business, is the need to enhance and improve our client experience and this App will help us do just that.

Download the Clientèle App where you will be able to do the following:
 • Get up to date information on our products and exciting loyalty benefit, Clientèle Rewards;
 • Add Clientèle Rewards to an existing policy;
 • Access and redeem your monthly Clientèle Rewards, these include savings on groceries, bus tickets, store gift cards and many other special offers;
 • Add a product or manage your existing policy;
 • Download your policy documentation and;
 • Submit a claim 24/7;
 • Buy your Clientèle Mobile SIM card and purchase discounted airtime & data.

Do you need assistance with using some of the features within the App? No problem, simply go to ‘Help’. Here you will access useful information that will guide you through the App. This App, is simple, easy, extremely user friendly and can be used immediately.

If you are an agent, log on to the App to access a digital sales platform where you can submit your applications digitally on the same day!

You can install the App on your smartphone or tablet. Once downloaded the App is free to use on all major SA networks, this means that Clientèle will pay for all the data that the App uses.

Download the Clientèle App now.

